## Task Format

Each task follows this format:

```
- [ ] [TASK-XXX] Brief description
```

**Components:**
- `[ ]` or `[x]`: Checkbox (mark when complete)
- `[TASK-XXX]`: Unique 3-digit task ID
- Brief description: What needs to be done

## Instructions

**Adding Tasks:**
1. Assign next available TASK-XXX ID
2. Add to **Pending** section
3. Keep descriptions concise (one line)

**Working on Tasks:**
1. Move task to **In Progress**
2. Update description with progress if needed
3. Move to **Completed** when done

**When to Update:**
- After completing features
- At session end
- After major milestones
